title: Nubar 2010 G188
description: nubar celebrates ten years of creating safe and innovative nail lacquers free of DBP (phthalate), formaldehyde, and toluene with nubar 2010. This fantastic shade consists of flakes of reflective glitter in a polychromatic base, and displays its many shades when worn alone as a sheer polish or layered over other nubar nail lacquers for a dramatic effect. The limit to nubar 2010's possibilities is your imagination!

title: MASH Set of 25 Nail Art Nailart Polish Stamp Stamping Manicure Image Plates Accessories Set Kit
description: The original MASH image plates, designed and created by MASH, in set of 25 image plates. Each plate measures about 1.8" with sanded edges for easy, comfortable handling and a protective nylon screen. All image plates are made from high grade stainless steel. All designs are from 2011 collection and you will get 25 image plates with 6 to 10 design on each. This bundle contains 25 stamping nail art image plates. Use this variety pack to have fun working on your nails or give them away as fabulous gifts to friends and family. Plate dimension is 5.5cm in diameter. Scraper & stamper not included, but available separately.How Nail Art Stamping Works1. Apply polish on image plate design.2. Using the scraper, scrape off the excessive nail polish.3. Stamp the image in rolling motion.4. Stamp design on nail smoothly.The plates pictured are the exact plates you will receive.

title: Opi Nail Lacquer, Not So Bora Pink, 0.5 Fluid Ounce
description: A rich, creamy pink with an exotic twist. Whenever you find yourself stuck in the office or in traffic staring down at your pink nails, this not so boring pink will have you longing for a tropical trip to Bora Bora.
